title: Sample Book, American Futures, Book #15, 1954
description: Contains 91 pages of 23 designs including designs by Lanette Scheeline and Ilonka Karasz. Design titles include: Bay Tree, Pine Tree, Mexican Street Scene, Bengal, Boundary, Monastera Leaf, Firmament, Veiling and Flowers, China Seas, Flying Birds, Bamboo Shadows, Grasses, Tiling, Persian Garden, Circus, Palisades Marble, Fancy Flowers, Spring Bulbs, Chinese Gauze, Cinderella, Daisy and Fern, Italian Book Paper, Pomegranate and Pineapple, Circle and Diamond and Emperor's Gold Fish. Each design appears in multiple colorways. Contains 2 children's papers. The use of photography, photoengraving and intaglio printing allows for a faithful reproduction. Many pages have been cut.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, American Futures, Book #15, 1954; Designed by Lanette Scheeline, Ilonka Karasz and Tina Leser; USA; machine printed on paper; 52.5 x 53.5 cm (20 11/16 x 21 1/16 in.); 1980-77-3-1/115
